# Memory folder (local notes)
Memory/
# BUT ship JUST the ONNX semantic loader chain (embed.py + its package __init__s) — it
# was silently caught by the case-insensitive "Memory/" rule, so semantic was OFF in the
# container (the loader never shipped). Idiom: re-include the dir, re-exclude its
# contents, then re-include ONLY the embedder files (not the 54-file memory subsystem,
# not __pycache__).
!src/groundtruth/memory/
src/groundtruth/memory/*
!src/groundtruth/memory/__init__.py
!src/groundtruth/memory/enrich/
src/groundtruth/memory/enrich/*
!src/groundtruth/memory/enrich/__init__.py
!src/groundtruth/memory/enrich/embed.py
.llm_config/
*.key

# local-only VM/GCP handoff — NEVER commit (contains project ID)
GT_VM_HANDOFF.md

# GCP rules doc — names the project, NEVER commit
gcp_fuckery.md

# run archive: keep records, not reproducible binaries
.claude/reports/runs/**/*.db
.claude/reports/runs/**/graph.db

# generated submission packages (re-create with package_submission.py)
submissions/**/trajs/
submissions/**/logs/

